{"featured_counts":0,"common_counts":1,"collapsed_counts":0,"reviewing_counts":0,"paging":{"is_end":true,"is_start":true,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/answers/564100838/root_comments?include=data%5B%2A%5D.author%2Ccollapsed%2Creply_to_author%2Cdisliked%2Ccontent%2Cvoting%2Cvote_count%2Cis_parent_author%2Cis_author\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=1\u0026order=normal\u0026status=open","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/answers/564100838/root_comments?include=data%5B%2A%5D.author%2Ccollapsed%2Creply_to_author%2Cdisliked%2Ccontent%2Cvoting%2Cvote_count%2Cis_parent_author%2Cis_author\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=0\u0026order=normal\u0026status=open","totals":1},"data":[{"id":568609981,"type":"comment","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/comments/568609981","content":"去哪里并不重要，关键在于如何定义未来。（既不愿接受现实的不堪渴望跳出厌恶的圈子，期待通过一场重塑之旅勇敢的去过另一种生活；又沉迷于其中自得其乐处于改变与犹豫的十字路囗徘徊不决，不断的质疑这种生活又是否是“我”想要的？）从围观成功者的惊羡到，狂热的追逐虚幻的诗与远方；片面的以为成功是衡量未来的唯一指标，却忽视了成长的内涵与节奏。当你能够理性的认识自己，并找到勾勒未来的参考系时，你已经在成长ing。每个人都有属于自己的舞台，不要因为没有掌声而轻易谢幕；也无须纠结于那些没有任何意义的结局。梦想是一个虚幻而沉重的话题，成长才是伴随你一生的事物如影随行。不是所有有价值的东西都可以量化衡量，也不是所有可以量化的东西都有价值。世界已经太吵，你需要听听自己内心的声音。","featured":false,"collapsed":false,"is_author":false,"is_delete":false,"created_time":1546330305,"resource_type":"answer","reviewing":false,"allow_like":true,"allow_delete":false,"allow_reply":true,"allow_vote":true,"can_recommend":false,"can_collapse":false,"author":{"role":"author","member":{"id":"3085fa6a967e32a302d2d6d45f38b537","url_token":"forge-81","name":"Forge","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-793ba433ff32dcb2f97b765c285ec4cb_r.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-793ba433ff32dcb2f97b765c285ec4cb_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/3085fa6a967e32a302d2d6d45f38b537","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false}},"vote_count":2,"voting":false,"disliked":false,"censor_status":0,"child_comment_count":0,"child_comments":[]}]}
